    "client_msg_id": "2d7d9a21-1286-4d72-a3f0-204a0948c6e7",
    "text": "Don't even how to begin without the whole in mind.  Maybe the main story is that I take seriously the question of machine intentionality from a John Searle point of view: where does meaning come from, how can you recognize it, and then I run with that.",
