  {
    "user": "UA14TGLTC",
    "type": "message",
    "ts": "1774455056.043869",
    "client_msg_id": "320bfec2-f863-47ab-983f-4152fb745ea0",
    "text": "Digging deep into my Feeling of Computing <https://wtaysom.github.io/imitation-engines/taking-our-jobs>, I return to Matz:\n&gt; Instead of emphasizing the what, I want to emphasize the how part: how we feel while programming. That’s Ruby’s main difference from other language designs. I emphasize the feeling, in particular, how I feel using Ruby. I didn’t work hard to make Ruby perfect for everyone, because you feel differently from me. No language can be perfect for everyone. I tried to make Ruby perfect for me, but maybe it’s not perfect for you.\nThe rest of that letter/novella there explores feeling with AI mostly, though there's a bunch of other stuff.  Zombies.  But it's mostly more suited for the <#C050QK4917D> channel.",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "rich_text",
        "block_id": "mCNxp",
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Digging deep into my Feeling of Computing "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://wtaysom.github.io/imitation-engines/taking-our-jobs"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ", I return to Matz:\n"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_quote",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Instead of emphasizing the what, I want to emphasize the how part: how we feel while programming. That’s Ruby’s main difference from other language designs. I emphasize the feeling, in particular, how I feel using Ruby. I didn’t work hard to make Ruby perfect for everyone, because you feel differently from me. No language can be perfect for everyone. I tried to make Ruby perfect for me, but maybe it’s not perfect for you."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "The rest of that letter/novella there explores feeling with AI mostly, though there's a bunch of other stuff.  Zombies.  But it's mostly more suited for the "
